  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  over 18 years of age

          -  a visual analog scale (VAS) equal to or higher than 30/100 ,

          -  having given consent to participation

          -  No contraindications to products used in the course of the study.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  having a vital distress that does not allow an adequate assessment of the intensity of
             the pain

          -  an inability to assess pain intensity according to the VAS,

          -  swallowing disorders or inability , or a contraindication or an allergy to the
             treatments used.
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
    <gender>All</gender>
